      "content": {
        "title": "Hip and Knee Osteonecrosis — Core Principles",
        "definition": "Ischemic death of subchondral bone leading to collapse and secondary arthritis, with etiologies including idiopathic, steroid, alcohol, and trauma.",
        "summary": "Ficat and Steinberg staging guide hip ON treatment from core decompression to arthroplasty. Collapse predicts poor joint-preserving outcomes."
      },
